-- Module Scripts:

local fake_module_scripts = {}

do -- nil.Dragify
	local script = Instance.new('ModuleScript', nil)
	script.Name = "Dragify"
	local function module_script()
		-- Scripted by [ Content Deleted ] (my old acc)
		-- Modified by SUS_Pro / tropim0dder (my current acc)
		--[[
		Usage:
			local dragify = require(path.to.module)
			
			-- To start dragify,
			dragify(<Instance: GuiObject> Frame_to_Move[, {.. <Instance: GuiObject> Frame_to_Drag ..}])
		--]]
		local UIS = game:GetService("UserInputService")
		function dragify(Frame,HoverFrames)
			local dragToggle = nil
			local dragSpeed = -math.huge
			local dragInput = nil
			local dragStart = nil
			local dragPos = nil
			local startPos = Frame.Position
			local hoverFrm = nil
			local function updateInput(input)
				local Delta = input.Position - dragStart
				local Position = UDim2.new(startPos.X.Scale, startPos.X.Offset + Delta.X, startPos.Y.Scale, startPos.Y.Offset + Delta.Y)
				local distance = (startPos.X.Offset - Position.X.Offset) + (startPos.Y.Offset - Position.Y.Offset)
				--game:GetService("TweenService"):Create(Frame, TweenInfo.new(0.30), {Position = Position}):Play()
				game:GetService("TweenService"):Create(Frame, TweenInfo.new(distance / (dragSpeed)), {Position = Position}):Play()
			end
			if HoverFrames then
				hoverFrm = HoverFrames
				for i,v in ipairs(hoverFrm) do
					v.InputBegan:Connect(function(input)
						if (input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton1 or input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.Touch) and UIS:GetFocusedTextBox() == nil then
							dragToggle = true
							dragStart = input.Position
							startPos = Frame.Position
							input.Changed:Connect(function()
								if input.UserInputState == Enum.UserInputState.End then
									dragToggle = false
								end
							end)
						end
					end)
					v.InputChanged:Connect(function(input)
						if input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseMovement or input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.Touch then
							dragInput = input
						end
					end)
				end
			else
				hoverFrm = Frame
				hoverFrm.InputBegan:Connect(function(input)
					if (input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton1 or input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.Touch) and UIS:GetFocusedTextBox() == nil then
						dragToggle = true
						dragStart = input.Position
						startPos = Frame.Position
						input.Changed:Connect(function()
							if input.UserInputState == Enum.UserInputState.End then
								dragToggle = false
							end
						end)
					end
				end)
				hoverFrm.InputChanged:Connect(function(input)
					if input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseMovement or input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.Touch then
						dragInput = input
					end
				end)
			end
		
			game:GetService("UserInputService").InputChanged:Connect(function(input)
				if input == dragInput and dragToggle then
					updateInput(input)
				end
			end)
		end
		
		return dragify
	end
	fake_module_scripts[script] = module_script
end

			return fake()

		return req(obj)
	end

	local UIS = game:GetService("UserInputService")
	local MarketplaceService = game:GetService("MarketplaceService")
	local Players = game:GetService("Players")

	function open()
	    tService:Create(MainFrame,TweenInfo.new(1),{
	        Position = UDim2.new(0.398, 0,0.848, 0)
	    }):Play()
	    tService:Create(ScreenShadowFrame,TweenInfo.new(0.9),{
	        BackgroundTransparency = 0.45
	    }):Play()
	end
	function close()
	    tService:Create(MainFrame,TweenInfo.new(1),{
	        Position = UDim2.new(0.398, 0,1.1, 0)
	    }):Play()
	    tService:Create(ScreenShadowFrame,TweenInfo.new(0.9),{
	        BackgroundTransparency = 1
	    }):Play()
	end
	function closeAllFrames()
	    for i,frame in pairs(Frames:GetChildren()) do
	        if frame:IsA("Frame") then
	            frame.Visible = false
	        end
	    end
	end
	function getGameInfo()
	    local info = {}
	    info.Name = MarketplaceService:GetProductInfo(game.PlaceId).Name
	    info.GameImage = MarketplaceService:GetProductInfo(game.PlaceId).IconImageAssetId
	    info.Players = game.Players:GetPlayers()
	    info.MaxPlayers = game.Players.MaxPlayers
	    return info

	function updateInfo()
	    local info = getGameInfo()

	    Frames.Home.Players.Text = "Players: "..#info.Players.."/"..info.MaxPlayers
	    Frames.Home.Welcome.Text = ("Hello, %s!"):format(localPlayer.Name)
	end

	        local tasky
	        tasky = task.spawn(function()
	            if notificationOn then
	                repeat task.wait(1)
	
	                until notificationOn == false
	            end
	            notificationOn = true
	            Notifications_Frame.Notification:Play()
	            local notification = Notifications_Frame.Notification_Template:Clone()
	            notification.Parent = Notifications_Frame
	            notification.Message.Text = message
	            notification.Visible = true
	            task.spawn(function()
	                notification.Hide.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
	                    notification:Destroy()
	                    notificationOn = false
	                    task.cancel(tasky)
	                end)
	            end)
	            notification.Position = notification.Position + UDim2.new(5,5,0,0)
	            notification:TweenPosition(notification.Position + UDim2.new(-5,-5,0,0),Enum.EasingDirection.Out,Enum.EasingStyle.Sine,1,true)
	            task.wait(duration)
	            notification:TweenPosition(notification.Position + UDim2.new(5,5,0,0),Enum.EasingDirection.Out,Enum.EasingStyle.Sine,2.5,true)
	            task.wait(1)
	            notification:Destroy()
	            notificationOn = false
	        end)
	    end
	end
